00:49:28,955 --> 00:49:33,485
The shaman, the child of that couple

438
00:49:33,496 --> 00:49:40,566
The children of that couple wouldn’t live in the past, always dying.

439
00:49:40,569 --> 00:49:49,769
Then one of their children, that shaman wanted to do that with their child.

440
00:49:49,787 --> 00:49:54,407
He wanted to send him along with the bladders.

441
00:49:54,412 --> 00:50:01,422
The shaman did that, [sending] him to the place of those living beings.

