00:50:01,433 --> 00:50:06,633
But he saw the place of those living beings as a house.

443
00:50:06,639 --> 00:50:13,589
When he arrived to the place of these seals in the winter

444
00:50:13,606 --> 00:50:18,596
They said some of them picked on him.

445
00:50:19,510 --> 00:50:26,430
That one sent with the bladders [was picked on by] those seals and spotted seals.

446
00:50:26,439 --> 00:50:29,249
They were different there.

447
00:50:29,262 --> 00:50:33,532
However, they said some of them treated him with love.

448
00:50:33,545 --> 00:50:38,325
They said that when after he went home and started hunting

449
00:50:38,330 --> 00:50:45,650
He would recognize those spotted seals or ringed seals.

450
00:50:45,662 --> 00:50:49,462
He recognized them like us people.

451
00:50:49,477 --> 00:50:58,697
They said that when he started hunting, since he recognized them, he would shoot arrows at them with great force.

